---
export const prerender = true;
---

<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <title>Miteinander — Nachbarschaftsverein Trier-Sued</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Miteinander — Nachbarschaftsverein in Trier-Sued. Repair Cafe, Nachbarschaftsgarten, Sprachcafe und mehr. Seit 2019." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Nunito+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    html { overflow-x: hidden; }
    /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
    *, *::before, *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
      color: #1C1917;
      background-color: #FFFBF5;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    img {
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255, 251, 245, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.06);
      padding: 0 2rem;
      height: 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: #2563EB;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .nav-logo-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #EA580C;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1C1917;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #2563EB;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      background: #2563EB;
      color: #fff !important;
      padding: 0.55rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-cta:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* Mobile menu */
    .nav-toggle {
      display: none;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
    }

    .nav-toggle span {
      display: block;
      width: 24px;
      height: 2.5px;
      background: #1C1917;
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-toggle {
        display: flex;
      }

      .nav-links {
        position: fixed;
        top: 72px;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 251, 245, 0.98);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        transform: translateY(-120%);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.08);
      }

      .nav-links.open {
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* ===== HERO — PEOPLE GRID ===== */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 120px 2rem 80px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #FFFBF5;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 3rem;
      min-height: 520px;
    }

    .hero-text {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5.5vw, 4.2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1C1917;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .hero-text h1 span {
      color: #2563EB;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #78716c;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.3rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle .divider {
      color: #d6d3d1;
      margin: 0 0.2rem;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: #EA580C;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 60px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.25);
    }

    .hero-cta:hover {
      background: #c2410c;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.35);
    }

    /* People grid in hero */
    .people-grid {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 480px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .people-grid .portrait {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 4px solid #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .people-grid .portrait:hover {
      transform: scale(1.08);
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .portrait-1 {
      width: 150px; height: 150px;
      top: 0; left: 10%;
    }

    .portrait-2 {
      width: 120px; height: 120px;
      top: 30px; right: 5%;
    }

    .portrait-3 {
      width: 170px; height: 170px;
      top: 140px; left: 35%;
      z-index: 3;
    }

    .portrait-4 {
      width: 110px; height: 110px;
      top: 180px; left: 5%;
    }

    .portrait-5 {
      width: 140px; height: 140px;
      top: 280px; right: 15%;
    }

    .portrait-6 {
      width: 100px; height: 100px;
      top: 340px; left: 25%;
    }

    /* Decorative dots */
    .dot {
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .dot-blue-1 {
      width: 18px; height: 18px;
      background: #2563EB;
      top: 60px; left: 2%;
    }

    .dot-orange-1 {
      width: 12px; height: 12px;
      background: #EA580C;
      top: 120px; right: 2%;
    }

    .dot-blue-2 {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      background: #2563EB;
      opacity: 0.5;
      top: 300px; left: 0;
    }

    .dot-orange-2 {
      width: 22px; height: 22px;
      background: #EA580C;
      opacity: 0.6;
      top: 400px; right: 8%;
    }

    .dot-blue-3 {
      width: 14px; height: 14px;
      background: #2563EB;
      opacity: 0.4;
      bottom: 20px; left: 45%;
    }

    .dot-orange-3 {
      width: 8px; height: 8px;
      background: #EA580C;
      top: 10px; left: 55%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .hero-subtitle {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .people-grid {
        height: 320px;
        order: -1;
      }

      .portrait-1 { width: 100px; height: 100px; top: 0; left: 5%; }
      .portrait-2 { width: 85px; height: 85px; top: 10px; right: 5%; }
      .portrait-3 { width: 120px; height: 120px; top: 80px; left: 30%; }
      .portrait-4 { width: 75px; height: 75px; top: 130px; left: 2%; }
      .portrait-5 { width: 95px; height: 95px; top: 190px; right: 10%; }
      .portrait-6 { width: 70px; height: 70px; top: 220px; left: 20%; }
    }

    /* ===== SECTION: WAS WIR TUN ===== */
    .section {
      padding: 100px 2rem;
    }

    .section-initiatives {
      background: #FFF7ED;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #EA580C;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #1C1917;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .initiatives-grid {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .initiative-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.05);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .initiative-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
    }

    .initiative-card:nth-child(1)::before { background: #2563EB; }
    .initiative-card:nth-child(2)::before { background: #16a34a; }
    .initiative-card:nth-child(3)::before { background: #EA580C; }
    .initiative-card:nth-child(4)::before { background: #9333ea; }

    .initiative-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.08);
    }

    .initiative-icon {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .initiative-card:nth-child(1) .initiative-icon {
      background: #dbeafe;
      color: #2563EB;
    }
    .initiative-card:nth-child(2) .initiative-icon {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #16a34a;
    }
    .initiative-card:nth-child(3) .initiative-icon {
      background: #ffedd5;
      color: #EA580C;
    }
    .initiative-card:nth-child(4) .initiative-icon {
      background: #f3e8ff;
      color: #9333ea;
    }

    .initiative-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #1C1917;
    }

    .initiative-detail {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #78716c;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .initiative-card p {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #57534e;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .initiatives-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    /* ===== SECTION: STIMMEN ===== */
    .section-voices {
      background: #FFFBF5;
    }

    .voices-grid {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .voice-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.05);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .voice-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.08);
    }

    .voice-portrait {
      width: 90px;
      height: 90px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin: 0 auto 1.2rem;
      border: 3px solid #FFF7ED;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.08);
    }

    .voice-quote {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #44403c;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .voice-quote::before {
      content: '\201E';
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #2563EB;
      opacity: 0.3;
      position: absolute;
      top: -1.5rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .voice-name {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #1C1917;
    }

    .voice-cta {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
    }

    .voice-cta p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #57534e;
    }

    .voice-cta a {
      color: #2563EB;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2563EB;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .voice-cta a:hover {
      color: #EA580C;
      border-color: #EA580C;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .voices-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        max-width: 400px;
      }
    }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    .footer {
      background: #1C1917;
      color: #a8a29e;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .footer-name {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #a8a29e;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }

    .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .hero-text {
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
    }

    .people-grid .portrait {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
    }

    .portrait-1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .portrait-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .portrait-3 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
    .portrait-4 { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
    .portrait-5 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .portrait-6 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
      <span class="nav-logo-dot"></span>
      Miteinander
    </a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Menu" onclick="document.querySelector('.nav-links').classList.toggle('open')">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#initiativen">Initiativen</a></li>
      <li><a href="#stimmen">Stimmen</a></li>
      <li><a href="#mitmachen" class="nav-cta">Mitmachen</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO — PEOPLE GRID -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Gemeinsam<br>geht <span>mehr.</span></h1>
        <div class="hero-subtitle">
          <span>Nachbarschaftsverein Trier-Sued</span>
          <span class="divider">&middot;</span>
          <span>Seit 2019</span>
          <span class="divider">&middot;</span>
          <span>180 Mitglieder</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#mitmachen" class="hero-cta">Mitmachen &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="people-grid">
        <!-- Diverse portraits from Unsplash -->
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face"
          alt="Nachbarin laechelnd"
          class="portrait portrait-1"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face"
          alt="Nachbar Portrait"
          class="portrait portrait-2"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face"
          alt="Vereinsmitglied"
          class="portrait portrait-3"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face"
          alt="Mitglied im Garten"
          class="portrait portrait-4"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face"
          alt="Junge Nachbarin"
          class="portrait portrait-5"
          loading="eager"
        />
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face"
          alt="Nachbar beim Repair Cafe"
          class="portrait portrait-6"
          loading="eager"
        />

        <!-- Decorative dots -->
        <span class="dot dot-blue-1"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-orange-1"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-blue-2"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-orange-2"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-blue-3"></span>
        <span class="dot dot-orange-3"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: WAS WIR TUN -->
  <section class="section section-initiatives" id="initiativen">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">Was wir tun</div>
      <h2>Vier Initiativen, ein Ziel</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="initiatives-grid">

      <div class="initiative-card fade-in">
        <div class="initiative-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Repair Cafe</h3>
        <div class="initiative-detail">Jeden 2. Samstag, Gemeindezentrum</div>
        <p>Kaputt heisst nicht weg. Unsere Reparatur-Profis helfen bei Elektronik, Textilien und Moebeln — kostenlos und mit Kaffee.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="initiative-card fade-in">
        <div class="initiative-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 20h10"/><path d="M10 20c5.5-2.5.8-6.4 3-10"/><path d="M9.5 9.4c1.1.8 1.8 2.2 2.3 3.7-2 .4-3.5.4-4.8-.3-1.2-.6-2.3-1.9-3-4.2 2.8-.5 4.4 0 5.5.8z"/><path d="M14.1 6a7 7 0 0 0-1.1 4c1.9-.1 3.3-.6 4.3-1.4 1-1 1.6-2.3 1.7-4.6-2.7.1-4 1-4.9 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nachbarschaftsgarten</h3>
        <div class="initiative-detail">Hochbeete am Petrisberg</div>
        <p>12 Hochbeete, eine Gemeinschaft. Hier waechst mehr als Gemuese — hier wachsen Freundschaften zwischen Generationen.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="initiative-card fade-in">
        <div class="initiative-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 18a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H9a2 2 0 0 0-2 2"/><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="4"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Sprachcafe</h3>
        <div class="initiative-detail">Deutsch ueben bei Kaffee & Kuchen</div>
        <p>Jeden Donnerstag treffen sich Menschen aus aller Welt, um gemeinsam Deutsch zu ueben. Ohne Druck, mit viel Kuchen.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="initiative-card fade-in">
        <div class="initiative-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="6" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Kinderflohmarkt</h3>
        <div class="initiative-detail">4x im Jahr</div>
        <p>Spielzeug, Kleidung, Buecher — von Familie zu Familie. Fair, guenstig und jedes Mal ein kleines Stadtteilfest.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: STIMMEN -->
  <section class="section section-voices" id="stimmen">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">Stimmen aus dem Verein</div>
